{"tid":2281260,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是暖午 跟住蕭生去四川","createTime":"2020-11-11T05:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T11:16:56.000Z","uid":8655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e30bcc1d110bea20faf682ecaaec83131b318c","tid":2281260,"uid":8655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"早排見到老蕭餐廳有新menu<br />\n今日咁撚凍 即刻落左去試呢個水煮滑嘔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多先上圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZOo1PS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZOo1PS.png&h=9b92d162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVAVSWL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVAVSWL.png&h=dbc99082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個飯好大個 填實曬個碗仲有個大山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n水煮嘔好大碗 夠曬飽肚有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個汁食落好濃厚 送飯一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd嘔cum住d配料 有菇芽菜韮黃萵筍 好撚足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n水煮汁辣度適中 食落件superdry好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老蕭個價都好合理 佢都係想打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655c15e3d920cc6f12c0b0b58cd4a99ed7af1c95","tid":2281260,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"幾錢???<br />\n晚巿客飯set?"},{"pid":"5d765aeffb1e9ca0bef6eecb043ca5a872b7c0d1","tid":2281260,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"廿幾度著乜superdry<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ba991e1cfc1451ee7074ad5c21be528471968c","tid":2281260,"uid":8655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"655c15e3d920cc6f12